<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer216932621642003876">Richard Wagamese was one of Canada&apos;s foremost Native authors and storytellers. He worked as a professional writer since 1979. He was a newspaper columnist and reporter, radio and television broadcaster and producer, documentary producer and the author of twelve titles from major Canadian publishers.<br/><br/> </span>
  <span id="freeText216932621642003876" style="display:none">Richard Wagamese was one of Canada's foremost Native authors and storytellers. He worked as a professional writer since 1979. He was a newspaper columnist and reporter, radio and television broadcaster and producer, documentary producer and the author of twelve titles from major Canadian publishers.<br /><br /> </span>
  <a data-text-id="216932621642003876" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

